                    </div>
                    <span>On behalf of the Iranian people, I would like to say to the Pahlavis that we are sorry. We messed up!<P>This book is a wonderful depiction of the great services the Shah gave to Iran and they way we, the people of Iran, betrayed him.<P>As the recent events in Iran show, the people of Iran are determined to bring down the brutal Islamic regime and restore dignity and sovereignty to the people.<P>We will get our country back from the facist Islamic dictators!</span>
                  
              
